{
  "text": "A few studies have been conducted to assess the effect of demographic factors on patient preference, and it was shown that younger individuals with a higher level of education require more information [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In our study subgroup analysis was not possible due to the small numbers in each group.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "15209077",
